{"tid":1774011,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"出發了","createTime":"2019-12-08T03:24:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-08T03:29:48.000Z","uid":223675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"ade09884a79f89588f171d27f0916dd1a64e97d9","tid":1774011,"uid":223675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T03:24:21.000Z","msg":"每一次嘅遊行，<br />\n無論有冇不反，<br />\n我都會當係最後一次，<br />\n因為同「香港人，報仇」唔同嘅係<br />\n黑警打死人真係唔係淨係口號<br />\n上星期開始我發現真係愈黎愈少人<br />\n掩護自然都係少左<br />\n今次個個打曬飛機話過百萬<br />\n係咪真係仲會有咁多人肯出黎<br />\n班狗又會唔會真係仲俾人出黎<br />\n出開黎嘅大家都知<br />\n知還知，都係要出黎<br />\nIf i do nothing,<br />\nthey will never forgive me<br />\n香港人，指意你地報仇就冇可能啦<br />\n可唔可以準時一次咁多。"},{"pid":"9be53e019b9af73b4111c87c6b8c3e64f51b5b16","tid":1774011,"uid":175590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T03:28:38.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">3點鐘 維園見 早D出門口呀</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/e3czX1e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fe3czX1e.jpg&h=afb0dc00&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"975ca3a47508f3699aeb3e29bd3e21b0454f7120","tid":1774011,"uid":223675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9be53e019b9af73b4111c87c6b8c3e64f51b5b16","tid":1774011,"uid":175590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T03:28:38.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">3點鐘 維園見 早D出門口呀</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/e3czX1e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fe3czX1e.jpg&h=afb0dc0